room, but in different parts

00:03:12.460 --> 00:03:14.960
of the library and
in our collections.

00:03:14.960 --> 00:03:19.340 position:56%
So we're really delighted to have
her with us, to have Connie with us,

00:03:19.340 --> 00:03:26.010 position:56%
