spelling] on the top of roofs.

00:47:36.660 --> 00:47:42.320
So that -- you know, that's --
and of course, salting fish,

00:47:42.320 --> 00:47:46.730
salting fish, but also
putting it in vinegar.

00:47:46.730 --> 00:47:51.020
