their yogurt to make it into fish.

00:48:20.200 --> 00:48:23.110
I mean excuse me, to
make it into cheese.

00:48:23.110 --> 00:48:26.250
So it's very dry, and
it's very salty.

00:48:26.250 --> 00:48:29.310
So you dehydrate it, and
it won't be as salty.

00:48:29.310 --> 00:48:33.690
